00059 void FusionCdfFileTest::testQCObjects(affxcdf::CCDFFileData &gcosCdf, affymetrix_fusion_io::FusionCDFData &fusionCdf)
00060 {
00061         affxcdf::CCDFQCProbeSetInformation gcosSet;
00062         affxcdf::CCDFQCProbeInformation gcosCel;
00063 
00064         affymetrix_fusion_io::FusionCDFQCProbeSetInformation fusionSet;
00065         affymetrix_fusion_io::FusionCDFQCProbeInformation fusionCel;
00066 
00067         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetHeader().GetCols() == fusionCdf.GetHeader().GetCols());
00068         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetHeader().GetRows() == fusionCdf.GetHeader().GetRows());
00069         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetHeader().GetNumQCProbeSets() == fusionCdf.GetHeader().GetNumQCProbeSets());
00070         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetChipType() == fusionCdf.GetChipType());
00071         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetFileName() == fusionCdf.GetFileName());
00072 
00073         int nps = gcosCdf.GetHeader().GetNumQCProbeSets();
00074         for (int ips=0; ips<nps; ips++)
00075         {
00076                 gcosCdf.GetQCProbeSetInformation(ips, gcosSet);
00077                 fusionCdf.GetQCProbeSetInformation(ips, fusionSet);
00078 
00079                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetQCProbeSetType() == fusionSet.GetQCProbeSetType());
00080                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetNumCells() == fusionSet.GetNumCells());
00081 
00082                 int nc = gcosSet.GetNumCells();
00083                 for (int ic=0; ic<nc; ic++)
00084                 {
00085                         gcosSet.GetProbeInformation(ic, gcosCel);
00086                         fusionSet.GetProbeInformation(ic, fusionCel);
00087 
00088                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetX() == fusionCel.GetX());
00089                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetY() == fusionCel.GetY());
00090                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetPLen() == fusionCel.GetPLen());
00091                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.IsPerfectMatchProbe() == fusionCel.IsPerfectMatchProbe());
00092                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.IsBackgroundProbe() == fusionCel.IsBackgroundProbe());
00093                 }
00094         }
00095 }
00096 void FusionCdfFileTest::testRegObjects(affxcdf::CCDFFileData &gcosCdf, affymetrix_fusion_io::FusionCDFData &fusionCdf)
00097 {
00098         affxcdf::CCDFFileHeader &gcosHeader = gcosCdf.GetHeader();
00099         affxcdf::CCDFProbeSetInformation gcosSet;
00100         affxcdf::CCDFProbeGroupInformation gcosGroup;
00101         affxcdf::CCDFProbeInformation gcosCel;
00102 
00103         affymetrix_fusion_io::FusionCDFFileHeader &fusionHeader = fusionCdf.GetHeader();
00104         affymetrix_fusion_io::FusionCDFProbeSetInformation fusionSet;
00105         affymetrix_fusion_io::FusionCDFProbeGroupInformation fusionGroup;
00106         affymetrix_fusion_io::FusionCDFProbeInformation fusionCel;
00107 
00108         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosHeader.GetCols() == fusionHeader.GetCols());
00109         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosHeader.GetRows() == fusionHeader.GetRows());
00110         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosHeader.GetNumProbeSets() == fusionHeader.GetNumProbeSets());
00111         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosHeader.GetNumQCProbeSets() == fusionHeader.GetNumQCProbeSets());
00112         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosHeader.GetReference() == fusionHeader.GetReference());
00113         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetChipType() == fusionCdf.GetChipType());
00114         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetFileName() == fusionCdf.GetFileName());
00115 
00116         int nps = gcosHeader.GetNumProbeSets();
00117         for (int ips=0; ips<nps; ips++)
00118         {
00119                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetProbeSetName(ips) == fusionCdf.GetProbeSetName(ips));
00120                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCdf.GetProbeSetType(ips) == fusionCdf.GetProbeSetType(ips));
00121         }
00122 
00123         for (int ips=0; ips<nps; ips++)
00124         {
00125                 gcosCdf.GetProbeSetInformation(ips, gcosSet);
00126                 fusionCdf.GetProbeSetInformation(ips, fusionSet);
00127 
00128                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetNumLists() == fusionSet.GetNumLists());
00129                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetNumGroups() == fusionSet.GetNumGroups());
00130                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetNumCells() == fusionSet.GetNumCells());
00131                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetNumCellsPerList() == fusionSet.GetNumCellsPerList());
00132                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetProbeSetNumber() == fusionSet.GetProbeSetNumber());
00133                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetProbeSetType() == fusionSet.GetProbeSetType());
00134                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosSet.GetDirection() == fusionSet.GetDirection());
00135 
00136                 int ng = gcosSet.GetNumGroups();
00137                 for (int ig=0; ig<ng; ig++)
00138                 {
00139                         gcosSet.GetGroupInformation(ig, gcosGroup);
00140                         fusionSet.GetGroupInformation(ig, fusionGroup);
00141 
00142                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetDirection() == fusionGroup.GetDirection());
00143                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetNumLists() == fusionGroup.GetNumLists());
00144                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetNumCells() == fusionGroup.GetNumCells());
00145                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetNumCellsPerList() == fusionGroup.GetNumCellsPerList());
00146                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetStart() == fusionGroup.GetStart());
00147                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetStop() == fusionGroup.GetStop());
00148                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetName() == fusionGroup.GetName());
00149                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetAlleleCode() == fusionGroup.GetAlleleCode());
00150                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetWobbleSituation() == fusionGroup.GetWobbleSituation());
00151                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetChannel() == fusionGroup.GetChannel());
00152                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosGroup.GetRepType() == fusionGroup.GetRepType());
00153                         
00154                         int nc=gcosGroup.GetNumCells();
00155                         for (int ic=0; ic<nc; ic++)
00156                         {
00157                                 gcosGroup.GetCell(ic, gcosCel);
00158                                 fusionGroup.GetCell(ic, fusionCel);
00159 
00160                                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetX() == fusionCel.GetX());
00161                                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetY() == fusionCel.GetY());
00162                                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetListIndex() == fusionCel.GetListIndex());
00163                                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetExpos() == fusionCel.GetExpos());
00164                                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetPBase() == fusionCel.GetPBase());
00165                                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetTBase() == fusionCel.GetTBase());
00166                                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetProbeLength() == fusionCel.GetProbeLength());
00167                                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel.GetProbeGrouping() == fusionCel.GetProbeGrouping());
00168                         }
00169                 }
00170         }
00171 }
